es are missing from the country list. #478](https://github.com/ForFunLabs/ElevenPublicBugsAndAsks/issues/478)\n-[world flag not selectable in list after tutorial #492](https://github.com/ForFunLabs/ElevenPublicBugsAndAsks/issues/492)\n-[log sending will stop even when forced #494](https://github.com/ForFunLabs/ElevenPublicBugsAndAsks/issues/494)\n-[floor indicator on portal is larger than other envs #500](https://github.com/ForFunLabs/ElevenPublicBugsAndAsks/issues/500)\n-[portal will not load correctly sometimes #502](https://github.com/ForFunLabs/ElevenPublicBugsAndAsks/issues/502)\n-[avatar images not shown in left panel #503](https://github.com/ForFunLabs/ElevenPublicBugsAndAsks/issues/503)\n-removed unusable spectator mode option from pico graphics settings\n\n\n**updates**\n-[add ball speed info in wall mode #495](https://github.com/ForFunLabs/ElevenPublicBugsAndAsks/issues/495)\n-Pico4 Ultra Controllers Added\n-Vivox disabled\n-continuing to work on replays:\n\tAs we know many of you would want to share replays with others, or post them on your social media, we are working on a way for the headset itself to provide .mp4 files\n\tAdditionally we are working on the UI for controlling the replays both with controllers and with the menu \n", "created_date": 1726206089, "id": "8108223599246826", "version": "0.304.0_2024.9.13.5.13.1.548", "version_code": 148367581, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "1995434190525828", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8145259962209856"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": []}, "change_log": null, "created_date": 1726204358, "id": "810809618259290